public class VisitNodesLinkedList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

Maintains all of the PointCells of a truck route. Title: VisitNodesLinkedList Description: This class maintains all of the PointCells of a truck route. The first and last PointCells are always the first depot and last depot of the truck route. Further information about each of the PointCells is stored in the PointCell class. collapseRoute

public void collapseRoute()
Trims the route to one PointCell per stop so that the optimization methods work better. Original route looked like this: (S# - student:pick up point, D - depot) D - S1 - S1 - S1 - S1 - S2 - S2 - S2 - S2 - S3 - S3 - S3 - S3 - D Now looks like this: D | S1 - S1 - S1 - S1 each of these students at same pick up point | S2 - S2 - S2 - S2 | S3 - S3 - S3 - S3 | D This will prevent the optimization functions from splitting visits to pick up points. These routes will have the same cost, because the distance has not changed. There is no additional distance for picking up multiple students from a pick up point.

expandRoute

public void expandRoute()
Expands the collapsed route to the original route. Extracts all the cells hidden by the collapseRoute() method.
